added comments to hints database. added custom __repr__ to prevent log spam. Split up the NamespaceActions - they were fundamentally incompatible concepts. NamespaceDictAction effectively transforms a key-value set of inputs into a nested defaultdict-style namespace, while NamespaceAction produces a list for each time the argument is used
